Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have a pet dog in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's so cute that I start talking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how when you talk to animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your voice gets all syrupy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Except this was in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I talk to my goldfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I lapse into baby talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I get talking to dogs and cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but people who talk to fish must be pretty darn lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's discrimination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the patronizing look!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When people call hot dogs... {Use "say" instead of "call".}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...wieners...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take a long time if I went into detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was definitely derived from a Chinese word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hand if you just thought of something naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gu***m is still ridiculously popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad also ***** it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of Gu***m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like V...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And W...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And X...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw 'em all when they first aired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call it passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or my duty as a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...would you watch Gu*dam: The Serial Murder Case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...or Detective Gunda* if they started airing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Gu***m fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that I have a **** to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,**** is kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a ***** you can't call it by a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All this talk about **ndam has reminded me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite appearances, I'm already *** years older than *muro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passed in a *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And in two more years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be the same age as B****t-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even imagine it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,B****t-san is a pretty *** character, even in the Gu***m world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for Ha**n-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you're ***** for your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I wouldn't use *** for a standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least say that I look ***** for my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our neighbor gave us something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A souvenir from vacation apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You grew up to be my kind of girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was a dangerous statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning already, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got wasted last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured I'd be out till noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.94,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,This is the morning news for Monday, July 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.81,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Early this morning, a man at a restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my day off!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.85,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...yelled: "Hey, this ramen sucks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I always plan on studying for tests at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I end up getting sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I asked Onee-chan for advice: {Changed due to direct speech in the next lines"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like horror movies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you watched one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that keep you up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how you crawled into my bed last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I didn't get sleepy after watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,An older sister knows just what to do. {Onee-san?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,once it's night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the slightest sound from behind would make me jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes it even harder to focus on studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I ended up not getting enough sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was tired in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But for someone who claims to dislike horror,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you watch those movies quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I chose to watch them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I rented this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too scary by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who can't stand it actually watch them more often, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they want to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, I really can't stand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the answer to this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked on it for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was going to ask Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really lucky to have upperclassmen to rely on in these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking with Iwasaki-san about that at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She has that much faith in me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is going to soon discover how the world is a very harsh place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever study together with K-neesan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a common situation in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When a boy and girl get together to study, they can never concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can't concentrate, you start fantasizing about stuff you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hidden side starts to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help with a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I happen to be busy, so ask Yui-neesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Study, study...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dirty move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe it's 'cause I went to a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I never learned this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, do you know this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask if you don't think I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll call Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Might be a bother for her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be a bother, since it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she never turn to her dad in these situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rely on me sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix ya real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in an age where corporal punishment isn't allowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,yet you often hit people like it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't hit just anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose my target very carefully, if you get my drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Else I could get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She actually said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Another crazy thing about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it doesn't make sense to ban corporal punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know these era names.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...why don't you ever ask your teacher!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question... {Tense issue: Had? Doesn't she rather "have" a question?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask away then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this rare item in a game I'm playing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always sweltering after a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a lot of instances of good weather after a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stormy weather flock together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what wasn't bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to make sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that was supposed to be a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kona-chan say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell what was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We watch the news and other stuff together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so why is she at Konata's level?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you people always have such perfect timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The pitcher is keeping an eye on the runner on second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the baseball game going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it'll probably go overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to change the recording time on the VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They could just give it a bigger time block to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody drags out their motions in pro baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't they be able to finish on time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if they did everything at a brisker pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Some fans like the game because of the pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the players need to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you used to school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm having a hard time with the huge homework load.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Third-years focus on studying for college testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so they don't have much homework, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.94,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Belly button showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you walk around dressed like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Yu-chan copies you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so hot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that thing the Diet's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool Biz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I'd gotten a reply yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading and I missed my stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your casual slip-ups are always so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure they just cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she's all embarrassed when she tries to make up for the mistake is killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cuter when you have some kind of shortcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So at your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I spilled it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You do stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem kinda dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who started talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I was the one who acted it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you pretend to be clumsy to score points with the customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a common stereotype,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll get in trouble with the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be like, "It's moe." and do it all the time. {Re-check for correctness.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Clumsy girls may be cute and moe,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's pretty annoying when they cause trouble in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you can just laugh it off in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You geeks can be really harsh sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get a perfect answer, courtesy of Look JT*,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a one-month journey through the tundra for the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.76,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Now, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On variety shows and quiz shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...they always have a bunch of prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.27,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I am currently at Earth's bellybutton...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.97,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ayers Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it to attract more contestants?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they get a big-name celebrity, the ratings will go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:51.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Today's mystery is located in wondrous Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:57.60,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here you will find kangaroos, koalas and other wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If they let the audience participate,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:02.05,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,This continent, separated long ago by tectonic movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave them the prizes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that boost ratings even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:06.19,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...has transformed into a holy land safe from foreign intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a direct way to do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was playing a game yesterday when I realized something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's our school idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this school idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Miss contest or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you would think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more theoretical in games, with stuff like personal bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Another exhausting day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should stay off the Internet tonight and hit the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to prioritize sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a sign that I'm getting old?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in school, I skipped sleep to have fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tamura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been making a lot of faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how when you're drawing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you tend to make the same faces as your characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you drew manga, Tamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mostly doujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of manga do you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal stuff like four panels...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Or romance stuff with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...game characters I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So hard to answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, I won 3,000 yen with a lottery ticket I randomly bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking how lucky I was that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:02.00,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But then my bicycle tire burst on the way to school, so I had to pay for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.44,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,And my box lunch was ruined, so I had to buy another one from a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.49,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,The money vanished so perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.17,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,My 3,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.79,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Truth is stranger than fiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure I can use this story for my manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The drawing hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...is an artist's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Must defend it with my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in a slump...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is probably one of my better recent ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people aren't going to notice the artist's habits or subtle touches...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tamura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my favorite pencil on my desk after I finished drawing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to borrow mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no good without it... {Isn't she speaking about the pencil here? Or is her pencil...female?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It just feels totally different...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencils are all the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that's how people would react...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ended up lost and couldn't get out for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tamura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are they thinking, wearing that in broad daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they hot wearing so much in summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So only people who understand can feel the agony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to message someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go write my name on the sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was up all night playing games with Konata-oneechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Suzuku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.16,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Suzuku-sama, party of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tamura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They called a different name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In these situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I always want to put down the name of my favorite character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda makes me feel closer to the character. {Is the "like" here really needed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find my people everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be all slender and tall like you, Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I admire you so much, Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll still grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, you'll grow even taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taller than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes against natural world order! {Just "natural order". Remove the "world".}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last one's totally off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamura-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kinda pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, today's the submission deadline for an upcoming event,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was up all night finishing... {Finishing what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sent it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I look at how hard I can work on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's yaoi? {HNNNNGGG, sorry had to do that}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which definition are you looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already on the nineteenth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're finally in the home stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the assistant, Shiraishi Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.66,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Net Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama appears to be in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Da-Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:48.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Can't do anything about adult circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Being on TV really puts a strain on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The stress really builds up after nineteen episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just soak in a spa and recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can win that prize they were talking about in the actual show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to start by appearing in the quiz show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveling is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to travel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Going some place you've never been really lightens your mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like to travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually been to many places!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've climbed Mt. Takao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been to Jogashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely the outdoors type!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you like to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When you want to calm yourself down these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing can beat a stroll through the splendor of a pristine forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A stroll through a pristine forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Must really calm the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Away from the hustle and bustle of the city, surrendering yourself to the tranquility of nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It heals both the body and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't nature great!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go on a walk through the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Minoru's Nature Tour's a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they'll come in handy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...am I going...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already been to the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the forests of Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The forests, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna drink some of that famous Fuji water,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so go get me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they sell that stuff at convenience stores!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want mine fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming with me, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The director and producer are sacrificing themselves to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.12,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.86,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:13.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:15.41,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a wonderful guest next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:16.09,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.47,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...here on Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can expect something great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:24.79,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:29.35,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we really need to go through all of this trouble to get rid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could have just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.73,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Part of my body is hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.16,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.94,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi Minoru here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.45,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,How a Man Should Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:54.30,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Aitsu no you ni naritai na!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:22:01.95,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Mae dake wo muite tsukisusume
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:08.40,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Ichido kimetara doko made mo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.98,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Kuraitsuitara hanasanai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:35.24,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Kokoro mo karada mo supopon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:58.52,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Kokoro mo karada mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:54.30,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} I wanna be like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:22:01.95,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Always looking ahead and moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:08.40,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Once you've made up your mind, never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.98,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Once you've grabbed on, never let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:35.24,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Body and soul are bare naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:58.52,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Body and soul are bare...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinkin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You get all excited before it starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but before you know it, it's over and nothing happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess nothing special ever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're not gonna have a long relationship with anybody you meet during fling season.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've still got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to Spend Summer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm available!
